Rhost Equiv: TEL_ANYTHING (@@power)

unkillable            Cannot be killed with the ‘kill’ command.
Rhost Equiv: NOKILL (@@power)

use_sql               Can call the SQL() function. (God-set only.)
Rhost Equiv: SQL is a 3rd party patch.

